Description: Welcome to this sun-filled, spacious home in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Sunnyside. This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house boasts high ceilings, hardwood floors, and an abundance of natural light throughout. The updated kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. The large backyard is perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying a quiet evening at home. With its proximity to top-rated schools, trendy restaurants, and easy access to public transportation, this Sunnyside gem has it all.
NeighborhoodDescription: Nestled between the vibrant neighborhoods of NoPa and the Mission, Sunnyside offers a balance of urban conveniences and suburban charm. With well-maintained parks, local cafes and shops, and a strong sense of community, Sunnyside is the perfect neighborhood for families and professionals alike. Easy access to public transportation, including the Sunnyside Muni Station, makes commuting a breeze.

Description: Welcome to this eco-friendly oasis nestled in the heart of Green Oaks. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts energy-efficient features such as solar panels and a well-insulated structure. Natural light floods the living spaces, highlighting the beautiful hardwood floors and eco-conscious finishes. The open-concept kitchen and dining area lead to a spacious backyard with a vegetable garden, perfect for the eco-conscious family. Embrace sustainable living without compromising on style in this Green Oaks gem.
NeighborhoodDescription: Green Oaks is a close-knit, environmentally-conscious community with access to organic grocery stores, community gardens, and bike paths. Take a stroll through the nearby Green Oaks Park or grab a cup of coffee at the cozy Green Bean Cafe. With easy access to public transportation and bike lanes, commuting is a breeze.

Description: Welcome to this spacious 4 bedroom home conveniently located in Sunnyvale. The home features hardwood floors throughout and plenty of windows with ample natural light. Upstairs has a humongous master suite and 2 additional large bedrooms with a full bath, the first level has an additional bedroom suite. Enjoy hosting in downstairs dining area or retreat outside to the large deck, perfect for entertaining. This home features a private backyard with lovely fruit trees.
NeighborhoodDescription: Sunnyvale is a vibrant neighborhood known for its sunny weather, friendly community and top-rated school district. This neighborhood includes a variety of grocery stores, restaurants and cafes within walking distance including the popular Sunnyvale Farmer's Market held on Saturday mornings. With easy access to public transportation and major highways, commuting around Silicon Valley is easy.

Description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom modern masterpiece in the heart of Culver City. This spacious home boasts an open floor plan with floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing for an abundance of natural light and breathtaking city views. The sleek and stylish kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances and plenty of counter space. Retreat to the private backyard oasis, complete with a pool, spa, and outdoor kitchen, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy luxury living in this prime Culver City location.
NeighborhoodDescription: Culver City is a vibrant and diverse community that offers the perfect blend of urban living and suburban charm. With a variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, there is always something to do. Take a short drive to the beach or explore nearby parks and hiking trails. With easy access to major freeways, commuting to Downtown LA is a breeze.
